## Post-Install Verification

```bash
# 1. Confirm slim wai.md
wc -l .claude/commands/wai.md
# Expected: < 60

# 2. Confirm wai-full.md exists
test -f .claude/commands/wai-full.md && echo "OK"

# 3. Confirm wai-closeout.md single 0c
grep -c "0c. Tender Pipeline Check" .claude/commands/wai-closeout.md
# Expected: 1

# 4. Confirm hook has track pre-write
grep -c "Pre-write track entry" .claude/hooks/session-start.sh
# Expected: 1
```

Expected outcome: wakeup with FRESH brief takes 0 tool calls and ~15s.
